Output demo/out/ui-module-card.gif

Require bash

Set Shell bash
Set FontSize 12
Set Width 960
Set Height 720
Set TypingSpeed 10 ms
Set Padding 18
Set Framerate 20

Type "$HOVEL_DEMO_UI_BIN show module-card --width 96"
Enter
Wait+Screen /Next: chain add mock-exploit-session-go@v0.0.0-example/
Sleep 2000 ms
